"required number of nodes is calculated based on the curve length and the "
"chainage length, after which the nodes are evenly distributed according to "
"this node count. "
msgstr "注意桩距并非曲线上节点最终间距，其用于计算节点数，最终节点间距将根据节点数重算以均匀分布在曲线上。"

#: ../src\yakxin\columbina\features\fillet\FilletDialog.java:77
